%h1 Books

:markdown

  A list of books I've read or an currently reading along with my favorite quotes.

%ul#books
  - data.quotes.each do |slug, b|
    
    %li.book
      .info
        %span.tags
          %span.tag.category= b.category
          %span.tag /
        %span.tags
          - b.tags.each do |tag|
            %span.tag.light= tag
      %h2.title
        %a{href: "/quotes/#{slug}.html"}= b.title
      %h4.author= b.author
